<span class="comment"><font color=#000000>Hackers hate it, but there are more programmers than "hackers".  Think about middle aged family men, career men.  They aren't all going to care as strongly or be able to quit.<p>Also even if you could convince all american talent to boycott it, there's a whole world of people out there who don't care at all, and just like America has been happy to sell censorship tech to the rest of the world for years, I'm sure the rest of the world would be happy to repay :)
